retty simple and easy to master but it's fun nontheless! Decision-making is so fast-paced! Every decision you make is meaningful, it will have effects almost immediatelly and game mechanics make sure to keep you constantly \"off-balance\" and on the verge of doom, so you wont have those waitingForSomethingToHappen-moments. It's like driving on a straingh road in a car that doesnt drive straight! Turn, turn, TURN!!! x)\nOn one hand it adds a little addrenaline to management. On the other hand, there wont be much pleasure from planning and executing. There is no planning, only executing! Instinctive management! :P I love it!\nThen there's the arena fights! So much pace, so much gore, so much intensity!... Sending your \"champion\" to the arena against tremendous odds. The fight starts, opponents rush to your champion. He takes hits, but he lands some good ones too. The crowd goes wild as the blood pours from each blow! One after another your champion's opponents fall. Legs, arms and heads fly all over the red sand and finally, from all the mess, your gadiator emerges victorious!!! The crowd is extatic! You go back to the ludo, with your gladiator, the price and the spoils. All of this in like.... 6 seconds! What a rush!\nThere is no story line to follow but there is a twist at the end of the game that will put of your choices on perspective. So even then the game surprises you.\nI could NOT end this without telling again about the soundtrack! By artist \"BIGNIC\". Powerfull, somewhat epic, modern but perfectly fitting the theme. In one word - AWESOME!\n", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "47939192", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1546123250, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1546121757, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198022535912", "playtime_forever": 1317, "last_played": 1546726571, "num_reviews":