e out anyone you send in within seconds.\n\nEven simply watching the auto-fights with your gladiators can be exhilarating. There is a lot on the line, and some matches can be won or lost by a hair. Its a great feeling to win a difficult match underequipped, and be pulled from the brink of bankruptcy. But conversely its defeating and infuriating to lose an easy fight to RNG shenanigans and go bankrupt because you didnt win the purse.\n\nRepetition set in fairly quickly for me. After about an hour of playtime I started to grow tired of the poor RNG mechanics. Its addicting though, easy to get into but difficult to master. The art direction is superb, the little pixel gladiators are adorable and fights are a spectacle.\n\n7/10", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "46529840", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1542959005, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1542953241, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198239753478", "playtime_forever": 449, "last_played": 1542953256, "num_reviews": 1, "num_games_owned": 48, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "Love the soundtrack", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "46520018", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1542953241, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1542949129, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198013459771", "playtime_forever": 1203, "last_played": 1551932101, "num_reviews": 1, "num_games_owned": 100, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 50}, "review": "Overall really impressed by this developer. For a stand alone (not sure if he has had some help but it seems it is mostly one person) he continues to pump out some fixes, additions, and improvements since release. For such a simple and cheap game, I have sunk man