emode a lot more fun for reasons above. Resource management (money, water, food, etc.) is less of a burden and getting Jupiter's Blessings buffs aren't really much of a pray-to-RNGesus mechanic. Besides the emotional turmoil you may endure, losing your best gladiator won't cost you the game! Spent much more time than I expected in Endless mode. It's fun to farm for the best gladiators, based on their personal stats (evasiveness, agression, amount of HP, attack/defend points). Call it survival of the fittest.\n\nYou can also piss off the Legate/Magistrate to get more challenging battles.\n\n\nBleed on!", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "41317963", "weighted_vote_score": "0.523809552192687988", "votes_up": 1, "steam_purchase": false, "timestamp_updated": 1523020330, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1523007866, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561197967136700", "playtime_forever": 2296, "last_played": 1552795914, "num_reviews": 50, "num_games_owned": 144, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 8}, "review": "Its Soccer manager with swords,dismemberment,beheadings,gore and lions :) \n\nIts a lot of fun and good mindless entertainment. \ngood value and worth the price", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "41315054", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1545461843, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1523002834, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198079221112", "playtime_forever": 1532, "last_played": 1523222741, "num_reviews": 17, "num_games_owned": 537, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "fun game, although a little bit more tutorial would be helpful", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "41314015", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": 