m events are also very boring.  Usually there's some story and you make some basic choices, then your stats either go up or down.\n\nFeedback to the devs:\n\n- Make the equipment system automatic the same way you can automatically train stats\n- Reduce the bonus from stats, just like in real life.  Even a trained fighter fighting peasants would eventually get caught with a blow and killed.\n- Instead of making the battles based on gladiators, set up several leagues so people can train their weak gladiators and strong ones at the same time, and make the battles harder over time.  If the player falls behind, GAME OVER, they shuold try again.\n- Because the boss fights have their own difficulty, make it very clear how difficult they are.\n\n\n\nWith some work this could be a very commendable game.", "comment_count": 1, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": false, "recommendationid": "41209617", "weighted_vote_score": "0.576411962509155273", "votes_up": 5, "steam_purchase": false, "timestamp_updated": 1522602544, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1522592295, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198190800398", "playtime_forever": 215, "last_played": 1527704596, "num_reviews": 33, "num_games_owned": 320, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "you can't survive at the end", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": false, "recommendationid": "41205856", "weighted_vote_score": "0.45267486572265625", "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1522592295, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1522587127, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198037986780", "playtime_forever": 1732, "last_played": 1551262363, "num_reviews": 4, "num_games_owned": 45, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "Great game highly recommend it, i already spent a full day on it in 2 days, very addictive and easy to play even on pro mode once you get 