 able to battle others online and progress my gladiator through fighting in manual-control-only bouts.\n\nSuggestions aside, this is a really fun game, and I highly recommend it if you're into tycoon games, especially if you dig the Roman vibe, pixel art, and jokes about kicking dudes in their scrotius ouchicus. I can see myself dumping some serious hours into this down the line.", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "33539790", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1500050996, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1500050889, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198032635738", "playtime_forever": 830, "last_played": 1512593650, "num_reviews": 3, "num_games_owned": 84, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "Brilliant", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "33539752", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1500050889, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1500021169, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198006894034", "playtime_forever": 386, "last_played": 1500020733, "num_reviews": 1, "num_games_owned": 269, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "For the most part I thoroughly enjoyed this game. That is until I completed it.\n\nThe ending is completely unsatisfying and is best decribed as 'a kick in the balls'. All your hard work and you have nothing to show for it. After that the playthrough just ends, I can't keep my gladiators I worked hard to train. I just have to start again.\nI know there is an endless mode, but it is severly broken as the battles from the very start are impossible (the enemies are about 12 levels higher no matter how many times I tried there was no way to win and therefore to progress further).", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": 