ur first few fights can sometimes be a total nightmare. On the other hand, once one of your gladiators has achieved 5 victories or so, he becomes more of a Terminator and just rapes anyone thrown in front of him after that.\n\nOne sufficiently leveled gladiator is enough to beat the entire game, alone. But, if you want the \"good ending,\" you'll need more than that--and leveling more than one guy can be tricky, for if you send one of them into the wrong fight he may not be coming back.\n\n\nDomina is not a very complex game, but it has some decent depth to it. It starts off from a great idea, and executes it quite well. Right now, at 3 bucks or so (I assume, for Americans and Europeans) I'd say it's a no-brainer. I paid 10 for it, and I'm glad I did--it was pretty fun struggling to finally get a solid playthrough, and I'm sure I'll come back to it soon to play some more.", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "33145890", "weighted_vote_score": "0.519999980926513672", "votes_up": 1, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1499020711, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1499020351, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198016678040", "playtime_forever": 1016, "last_played": 1550440648, "num_reviews": 9, "num_games_owned": 173, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "Like Gladiator games?\nLike simulation games?\nLike to manage stuff?\n\nThen this game is for you. Buy it :)", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "33145553", "weighted_vote_score": "0.489881962537765503", "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1499020351, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1499020286, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198065880185", "playtime_forever": 1141, "last_played": 1536016068, "num_reviews": 1, "num_games_owned": 42, "playtime_last_two_week