akedowns with getting a scratch. This gladiator then went on to defeat all 12 regional champions.\n\nCombat is fun as HELL the amount of fun I've had seeing these pixel men beat the lights out of eachother is substantial. Mind Control being unlocked early in the tech tree is a good part on the developer. Researching far enough will allow your guys to throw swords, roll into people and hurt them as well as a lot of defense buffs. Lions being available for use is great but I wish that lions on the enemy team would appear a lot more. Class wise it is a bit shallow. 3 classes with set out playstyles: Want long reach? Retarius. Want lotsa damage? Murmillo. Tough tank? Thraex. Having more variety in the class system would raise this games standard to something magical.\n\nOverall this game is brilliantly bloody and fun. Maybe not suitable for 9 and older though.\nRating: 9.5/10\nBetter if: More classes", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "32955571", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": false, "timestamp_updated": 1498680283, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1498678597, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198101723830", "playtime_forever": 750, "last_played": 1515624432, "num_reviews": 2, "num_games_owned": 42, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "Awesome game, massively addictive. Great humour throughout and an interesting setting.", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "32954161", "weighted_vote_score": 0, "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": false, "timestamp_updated": 1498678597, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1498677378, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561197987323362", "playtime_forever": 317, "last_played": 1498676984, "num_reviews": 31, "num_games_owned": 810, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": " Caught a bit of Do