ligible. Don't get me wrong, there is good occlusion like we see in FTL event dialogs, and this game captures some of that, but it also has quite a bit of poorly done occlusion where you're not quite certain for example whether the favour of the legit and magistrate actually effect the matches. All told, I think this game is worth the $10 for the fun you'll have pretending to be a roman gladiator/ludas owner, and trying to figure out how to beat the game. Especially so if the developer continues to do updates like he has in the days after the release.", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "30954694", "weighted_vote_score": "0.545454561710357666", "votes_up": 3, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1491454318, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 0}, {"timestamp_created": 1491364370, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561198355596446", "playtime_forever": 670, "last_played": 1518367021, "num_reviews": 6, "num_games_owned": 62, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "This game is awsome i have had tis game since it came out and the game is really cool i love it so much", "comment_count": 0, "received_for_free": false, "voted_up": true, "recommendationid": "30954491", "weighted_vote_score": "0.4912148118019104", "votes_up": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "timestamp_updated": 1491364370, "written_during_early_access": false, "votes_funny": 1}, {"timestamp_created": 1491362577, "language": "english", "author": {"steamid": "76561197979402731", "playtime_forever": 624, "last_played": 1491656874, "num_reviews": 73, "num_games_owned": 938, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0}, "review": "Fun to watch on twitch but not so fun to play, very random and insane hard, i played on easy and got my ass handed to me most of the time during my 4 hours of playing on easy.I more or less figured out how to play and managed to get 10 gladiators with more or less decent gear before they all got slaughtered in a 10